        "setup": "Register an OAuth client in Fugle's developer flow and use the resulting `client_id` with PKCE. The authorize endpoint is [https://www.fugle.tw/api/v2/oauth/authorize](https://www.fugle.tw/api/v2/oauth/authorize); the token endpoint is [https://www.fugle.tw/api/v2/oauth/token](https://www.fugle.tw/api/v2/oauth/token). The auth server requires `response_type=code`, `redirect_uri`, `code_challenge`, and `code_challenge_method=S256`. Request only the scopes you need: `note:read`, `note:write`, `watchlist:read`, `watchlist:write`, `data:read`, `price-alert:read`, `price-alert:write`.",
